## ðŸŽ“ Key Teaching Insight

G â†’ R â†’ C works as a **feedback loop**:  

- Governance defines strategy  
- Risk identifies where that strategy must focus  
- Compliance ensures accountability â€” and influences new governance decisions  

When these are done **together**, security is strong and intentional.  
When done separately â€” gaps and inefficiencies emerge.

